   "source": [
    "# XGBoost Model — Diabetes Risk Classification\n",
    "\n",
    "**Project:** Diabetes Risk Segmentation & Decision Support System  \n",
    "**Framework:** CRISP-DM — Modeling Phase  \n",
    "**Target:** `diabetes_stage` (multi-class: Gestational, No Diabetes, Pre-Diabetes, Type 1, Type 2)  \n",
    "**Model:** XGBoost Classifier  \n",
    "\n",
    "This notebook covers:\n",
    "1. Data preparation via `data_preprocessing.py`\n",
    "2. XGBoost baseline training\n",
    "3. Hyperparameter tuning via RandomizedSearchCV\n",
    "4. Evaluation (Accuracy, Classification Report, Confusion Matrix, ROC-AUC, Log-Loss)\n",
    "5. Native feature importance\n",
    "6. Learning curves — overfitting / underfitting diagnostics\n",
    "7. Final model identification & saving"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "markdown",
   "id": "xgb-imports-md",
   "metadata": {},
   "source": [
    "## 1. Imports & Setup"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "code",
