   "source": [
    "## 2. Data Preparation\n",
    "\n",
    "`run_pipeline()` executes the full CRISP-DM data preparation sequence:\n",
    "- Column standardisation (lowercase, strip whitespace)\n",
    "- Duplicate removal & missing value imputation\n",
    "- Feature engineering (`age_group`, `bmi_category`, `bp_category`)\n",
    "- Train/test split (stratified, 80/20)\n",
    "- IQR outlier removal **on training set only** (prevents data leakage)\n",
    "- Preprocessing pipeline fit on train, transform on both sets\n",
    "- Target label encoding"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "code",
   "execution_count": 3,
   "id": "xgb-data",
   "metadata": {},
   "outputs": [
