   ],
   "source": [
    "xgb_base = XGBClassifier(\n",
    "    objective='multi:softprob',\n",
    "    num_class=n_classes,\n",
    "    n_estimators=100,\n",
    "    learning_rate=0.1,\n",
    "    max_depth=6,\n",
    "    eval_metric='mlogloss',\n",
    "    random_state=42,\n",
    "    n_jobs=1\n",
    ")\n",
    "xgb_base.fit(\n",
    "    X_train_proc, y_train,\n",
    "    sample_weight=sample_weights,\n",
    "    eval_set=[(X_test_proc, y_test)],\n",
    "    verbose=False\n",
    ")\n",
    "\n",
    "y_pred_xgb_base  = xgb_base.predict(X_test_proc)\n",
    "y_proba_xgb_base = xgb_base.predict_proba(X_test_proc)\n",
    "\n",
    "xgb_base_acc = accuracy_score(y_test, y_pred_xgb_base)\n",
    "xgb_base_roc = roc_auc_score(y_test, y_proba_xgb_base, multi_class='ovr', average='macro')\n",
    "xgb_base_ll  = log_loss(y_test, y_proba_xgb_base)\n",
    "\n",
    "print(f'XGBoost Baseline — Accuracy: {xgb_base_acc:.4f} | Macro ROC-AUC: {xgb_base_roc:.4f} | Log-Loss: {xgb_base_ll:.4f}')\n",
    "print('\\nClassification Report:')\n",
    "print(classification_report(y_test, y_pred_xgb_base, target_names=classes))"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "markdown",
   "id": "xgb-tune-md",
   "metadata": {},
   "source": [
    "## 4. Hyperparameter Tuning — RandomizedSearchCV\n",
    "\n",
    "Key XGBoost knobs:\n",
    "- **`n_estimators`** — number of boosting rounds\n",
    "- **`max_depth`** — tree depth (controls model complexity)\n",
    "- **`learning_rate`** — step shrinkage (trade accuracy for robustness)\n",
    "- **`subsample`** — row sub-sampling (reduces overfitting)\n",
    "- **`colsample_bytree`** — column sub-sampling per tree\n",
    "- **`min_child_weight`** — minimum sum of instance weight in a leaf\n",
    "- **`gamma`** — minimum loss reduction for a split\n",
    "\n",
    "> `n_jobs=1` on the model and `n_jobs=-1` on the search avoids CPU oversubscription on large datasets."
   ]
  },
